  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 70ee8ab7554a13a4d9d7566ffc03ae8b, type: 3}
  m_Name: The Magician
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::FlightPaper.ProjectSorrow.Encounters.EncounterScriptableObject
  id: 3
  title: The Magician
  description: "A man is performing card tricks for anyone who will give him the
    time. \n\nDespite your best efforts, he manages to corner you. After performing
    a flashy shuffle for you, he extends the deck out toward you.\n\n\"Pick a card.
    Any card!\""
  options:
  - title: Pick a top card
    description: Earn <color=#D2D2D2>4 of Diamonds</color>
    requirement: Requires an available item slot
    conclusion: 'After giving the deck a quick tap and saying something cheesy, the
      man reveals the entire deck to now be the same card.


      He insists you
      keep the card as a lucky charm.'
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 03d764d3620ba4e4fb58518dd8c219bb, type: 2}
    consumable: {fileID: 0}
    tag: 
  - title: Pick a middle card
    description: Earn <color=#00C300>Flashcard</color>
    requirement: Requires an available item slot
    conclusion: '"Ha! How did that get in there?"


      The man then pulls identical
      flashcards from various places. He insists you keep yours and tell your friends
      about his antics.'
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f23b7c5750fba1947baca8243f5d5a4d, type: 2}
    consumable: {fileID: 0}
    tag: 
  - title: Pick a bottom card
    description: Earn <color=#00C300>Wheel of Fortune</color>
    requirement: Requires an available item slot
    conclusion: '"I bet you weren''t expecting a tarot reading!"


      The man
      proceeds to tell you that you''ll experience a great change in the near future.
      You hope that it is a change for the better.'
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 11400000, guid: db66db4e868af244fafbafa4d7d0cc2d, type: 2}
    consumable: {fileID: 0}
    tag: 
  - title: Walk away
    description: <color=purple>+1</color> arrogance
    requirement: 
    conclusion: 'You don''t have time for such shenanigans and decide to proceed
      to the bar.


      Based on the magician''s reaction, you don''t think this
      is the first time this has happened to him this evening.'
    isHidden: 0
    item: {fileID: 0}
    consumable: {fileID: 0}
    tag: Arrogance
  minRound: 0
